divs: Sighting Detailsit has been occurring everynight for about a month,I like to watch the night skies one night i seen a strobing what i thought was a star and i had my significant other look through the binoculars as well,if there is a clear night you can see them last night there was about twenty of them,i cant believe people are not seeing them.i was standing in my driveway looking in the direction west towards thee ocean when i seen what i thought was a star but it was too long so i got the binoculars out and looked throuh them and seen they were strobing multi colored lights even though they were strobing the object was stationary.
